Review Text: I ordered a dress from Gala celebration. They sent a Google form for custom fitting. Wt a waste of time, if you guys don't want to deliver.
Developer Reply Text: Hi Utkarsha, We are sorry to hear this. We take measurements for custom fitting via 2 means- either we send our fitting expert or we send a simple Google form where you can enter them. Either of it is done with your consent immediately after you place the order which was what we did in this case too. Hope you give us another shot. Love Team Flyrobe
